        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_mamba.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 853b4070-99b1-45da-938b-6fa7947eb7cd).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47, and welcome back to Sapienza. Today we only have one target, Marco Abiatti. We don&apos;t know much about Abiatti, but what I do know is that he has some important information that is a danger to all of Europe. The client doesn&apos;t even want us to know the plot, he just wants us to assassinate Abiatti before he gets on stage and gives the speech where he&apos;s going to expose himself. You have about 7 minutes before Abiatti&apos;s turn to speak. I&apos;d recommend the sniper rifle, 47. Good luck.",
